sec.p:
Schwank ( 1990 )
provided taxonomic keys for the freshwater species of Heterolepidoderma , but seven additional new taxa have been described since his publication (
Grosso & Drahg 1991 ;
Kisielewski 1991 ;
Balsamo & Fregni 1995 ;
Kånneby 2011 ; Kånneby et al.2012 ; present study) and two species have been considered species inquirenda (
Balsamo et al.2009 ), summing up to a total of 22 valid species. A revised key therefore seems appropriate.

